{"tid":8214,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"家中馬兒突暴怒 男童陰莖慘遭咬斷","createTime":"2016-11-28T08:24:04.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-28T11:08:56.000Z","uid":12709,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5dfa37a010f02024e04d3df3d953887c2ce81969","tid":8214,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T08:24:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2015-09-06/590/20150906001223.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2015-09-06%2F590%2F20150906001223.jpg&h=7fc822a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n烏克蘭北部發生一宗罕見意外。一名男童在後院騎腳踏車時，突然被家中飼養的馬撞至跌在地上，陰莖更慘被咬甩，他的父親事後把它拾回，醫生進行手術植回，未知能否回復正常功能。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2015-09-06/590/20150906001225.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2015-09-06%2F590%2F20150906001225.jpg&h=b9a72b2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n報導指出，男童騎腳踏車在馬前經過，馬匹突發怒向他攻擊。小童痛極，立即找父親，父親先用雙手按著傷處為兒子止血，然後找來救護車，並成功尋回兒子斷掉的陽具。主診醫生已為小童進行手術植回，但需要一段時間才知道它可否回復正常功能。"},{"pid":"cc9f5f68602bd3705c33624a5cff794f2fcc4d59","tid":8214,"uid":21283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T08:25:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6557073ffc90bcd9948145f5f8e6f284e2facc95","tid":8214,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T11:05:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"101007727649b12f0b23734359cc661d8e09f053","tid":8214,"uid":8934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T11:08:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=Q-EStdvjd_8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQ-EStdvjd_8&d=At%2FmxAuYDGgbNgvGzD8Mh8W%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=5dbe55a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">htt